NK032(khi)001:1: // rdzogs pa chen po klong sde'i rgyud lung gi rtsa ba gces par btus pa bzhugs so //
NK032(khi)001:3: ma h+aa san+d+hi ma h+aa +aa brta pra s+aa ra ni r+aa dza tan+t+ra gar+b+ha /
NK032(khi)001:5: rdzogs pa chen po klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud kyi snying po /
NK032(khi)001:6: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)001:7: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis thugs kyi dgongs pa ma nor bar gsung pa /
NK032(khi)001:9: gzhi 'khor 'das grub pa med pa'i klong gi dgongs pa dang /
NK032(khi)001:10: lam lta sgom spyod 'bras ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i klong gi dgongs pa dang /
NK032(khi)001:11: 'bras bu mthar thug sku gsum dbyer med klong gi dgongs pa'o //
NK032(khi)001:13: thig le gcig gi ngo bo la //
NK032(khi)001:14: sangs rgyas ma rgyas med par gcig /
NK032(khi)001:15: sangs rgyas 'bras bu btags pa yang //
NK032(khi)001:16: thob pa'i yon tan gzhan na med //
NK032(khi)001:17: sems nyid klong chen de yi ru //
NK032(khi)001:18: sems can rgyu ru snang ba yang //
NK032(khi)001:19: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs logs na med //
NK032(khi)001:20: bya bral klong chen de yi rtsal //
NK032(khi)001:21: rgyu 'bras med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK032(khi)001:22: sangs rgyas sems can dbyer med de //
NK032(khi)001:23: de la rang gis bcos su med //
NK032(khi)001:24: rgyu rkyen 'bras bur btags pa yang //
NK032(khi)001:25: dkri drang don gyis bstan par zad //
NK032(khi)001:30: 1ma nor ba yi chos nyid la //
NK032(khi)001:33: de bzhin nyid kyi gnas 'di la //
NK032(khi)001:34: yengs dang ma yengs med pa dang //
NK032(khi)001:35: g.yo dang mi g.yo med pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:36: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'di las med //
NK032(khi)001:37: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK032(khi)001:38: ma nor lta bas thag bcad pa'i klong /
NK032(khi)001:39: ma bcos sgom pas nyams su blang ba'i klong /
NK032(khi)001:40: ma byas spyod pas bogs dbyung ba'i klong /
NK032(khi)001:41: ma 'gags 'bras bu nyams su myong ba'i klong gi dgongs pa'o //
NK032(khi)001:43: rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK032(khi)001:44: rgyu 'bras rdzas su rtog pa ni //
NK032(khi)001:45: grub mtha' ngan pas bcings pa ste //
NK032(khi)001:46: 'khrul pas don las gol ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:47: bstan zhing brjod pa rab tu dka' //
NK032(khi)001:48: klong chen 'khyil ba'i mkha' dbyings ni //
NK032(khi)001:49: kun gyi gnas chen yin pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:50: yul la spyod cing rnam par yan //
NK032(khi)001:51: 'khrul pas don la gol ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:52: tshad mas bshigs pas mi shigs te //
NK032(khi)001:53: klong chen rang gi mthu yis grol //
NK032(khi)001:54: rtog mtha' bcad pas mi chod de //
NK032(khi)001:55: klong chen rang gi stobs kyis gcod //
NK032(khi)001:56: rang sems tshad ma'i gding ldan pa'i //
NK032(khi)001:57: 'gyur med don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK032(khi)001:58: lung rig don gyi bya ra bas //
NK032(khi)001:59: log rtog lkugs pa rdul du brlag /
NK032(khi)001:61: phyir mi ldog pa don gyi lung //
NK032(khi)001:62: mtha' ru mi stong 'dzin par byed //
NK032(khi)001:63: shes rab mtshungs med rig pa'i tshad //
NK032(khi)001:64: yul du mi gcod mnyam pa'i klong //
NK032(khi)001:65: kun gyis thun mong ma yin pas //
NK032(khi)001:66: 'di la btsal zhing bsgrub tu med //
NK032(khi)001:68: dka' thub dka' spyod mi dgos te //
NK032(khi)001:69: 'di la sbyang zhing bgrod du med //
NK032(khi)001:70: ma bcos rang sa nyid du gsal //
NK032(khi)001:71: stobs ldan chags pa'i yul med pas //
NK032(khi)001:72: lam stegs 'bras bu thob tu med //
NK032(khi)001:74: byar med ye klong don 'di la //
NK032(khi)001:75: tshig tu mtshon du gdags gzhi med //
NK032(khi)001:76: yul du bya ru dmigs gtad med //
NK032(khi)001:77: ting 'dzin bzlas pa bya mi dgos //
NK032(khi)001:78: ci zhig bsgrub cing gang la gnas //
NK032(khi)001:79: byar med don la sngags su med //
NK032(khi)001:80: ji ltar snang zhing grags pa'i chos //
NK032(khi)001:81: rang las byung bas rang gi rgyan //
NK032(khi)001:82: gzhan du 'dzin pa rtog pa'i blo //
NK032(khi)001:83: de la zhen pa 'khrul pa'i sems //
NK032(khi)001:84: gzung 'dzin med na grol ba'i lam //
NK032(khi)001:85: rang sems de ru ma shes na //
NK032(khi)001:86: thabs chen gzhan du btsal du med //
NK032(khi)001:87: ston pa rang du ma shes na //
NK032(khi)001:88: kun tu bzang po logs na med //
NK032(khi)001:89: bstan pa rang du ma shes na //
NK032(khi)001:90: theg pa'i rnam grangs gzhan na med //
NK032(khi)001:91: 'khor rnams rang du ma shes na //
NK032(khi)001:93: dus rnams rang du ma shes na //
NK032(khi)001:94: re ba'i thag pa chod mi 'gyur //
NK032(khi)001:95: de ltar gnas pa'i don 'di la //
NK032(khi)001:96: 'ching dang grol ba gnyis su med //
NK032(khi)001:97: gzhal bya 'jal byed tshig gi mtha' //
NK032(khi)001:98: dmigs pa'i yul la rtogs dpyod byed //
NK032(khi)001:99: yid dpyod shes pa don du 'dzin //
NK032(khi)001:100: bskal pa bye ba brgyar bgrangs kyang //
NK032(khi)001:103: rnam dag lam chen kun 'byung phyir //
NK032(khi)001:104: skye ba'i sgo yang dgag tu med //
NK032(khi)001:105: ma bkag byang chub sems kyi klong //
NK032(khi)001:106: byang chub sems la skye ba med //
NK032(khi)001:107: 'chi ba'i lam yang bcad du med //
NK032(khi)001:108: ma bcad byang chub sems kyi klong //
NK032(khi)001:109: byang chub sems la 'chi ba med //
NK032(khi)001:110: skye shi med pa'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK032(khi)001:111: rang la gnas pas btsal mi dgos //
NK032(khi)001:112: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar thug sku gsum dbyer med klong gi dgongs pa ni /
NK032(khi)001:113: yod dang med pa'i khyad par las //
NK032(khi)001:114: rtag dang chad pa'i gol sar byung //
NK032(khi)001:115: mtha' gnyis dbyings la mi gnas phyir //
NK032(khi)001:116: mi rtog ye shes klong du thim //
NK032(khi)001:117: rang byung ye shes sku brnyes pas //
NK032(khi)001:118: mtha' rnams kun gyi mi nub phyir //
NK032(khi)001:119: rgyal mtshan nor bu rin po che //
NK032(khi)001:120: khyad par 'phags pa mchog gi lam //
NK032(khi)001:121: bla med bde gshegs rnams kyi thugs //
NK032(khi)001:122: sa bcu byang chub sems dpa'i sku //
NK032(khi)001:123: 'gro drug sems can rnams kyi lus //
NK032(khi)001:124: gter chen 'di las gzhan med pas //
NK032(khi)001:125: kun gyi rang bzhin 'di ru gcig /
NK032(khi)001:126: gcig po ma nges phyogs dang bral //
NK032(khi)001:127: nam mkha' lta bur khyab pa'i klong //
NK032(khi)001:128: mtshan ma med pa'i dbyings su thim //
NK032(khi)001:129: chos kyi snying po dbyings kyi klong //
NK032(khi)001:130: kun 'byung nor bu rin po che //
NK032(khi)001:131: bgrod med rtsol bral rig pa'i klong //
NK032(khi)001:132: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid la //
NK032(khi)001:133: kha dog dbyibs kyang gzung du med //
NK032(khi)001:134: yul dang gnas kyang bstan du med //
NK032(khi)001:135: thams cad de yis bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:136: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi yum //
NK032(khi)001:137: thams cad gnas su med la gnas //
NK032(khi)001:138: kun kyang bsten du med la brten //
NK032(khi)001:139: phu bgrod mda' bgrod gar phyin kyang //
NK032(khi)001:140: sems nyid klong las ma g.yos pas //
NK032(khi)001:141: kun gyi dur khrod chen po'i dbyings //
NK032(khi)001:142: mtshan ma dbyings su dag pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:143: rnam dag chen po nyams dag'i klong //
NK032(khi)001:144: yon tan thams cad 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:145: nor bu rin chen spungs pa'i khrod //
NK032(khi)001:146: yul dang yul can med pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:147: bsam gyis mi khyab sku gsung thugs //
NK032(khi)001:148: rgyal ba kun gyis rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:149: dgongs pa ma lus phul du phyin //
NK032(khi)001:151: lhan cig skyes kyang ngo ma shes //
NK032(khi)001:152: blo chung rnams kyis ma go bas //
NK032(khi)001:153: brtags dang dpyad pa'i mtha' las grol //
NK032(khi)001:154: de ni blo ldan gang zhig gis /
NK032(khi)001:155: gzhan du mi blta rang du blta //
NK032(khi)001:156: bltas pas mthong ba med pa de //
NK032(khi)001:157: mnyam pa nyid kyi don mthong yin //
NK032(khi)001:158: sku gsung mchog tu gyur pas na //
NK032(khi)001:159: chos kyi sku yi ngang la gnas //
NK032(khi)001:160: blang dor med dang skye 'gag med //
NK032(khi)001:161: rnal 'byor chen po zhi ba'i sa //
NK032(khi)001:162: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po yin //
NK032(khi)001:163: med pa'i snying po nam mkha'i rdzong //
NK032(khi)001:164: yod pa'i snying po rdo rje'i sku //
NK032(khi)001:165: gnyis med snying po phyogs dang bral //
NK032(khi)001:166: snying po byang chub sems 'di la //
NK032(khi)001:167: cir yang mtshon du med pa'i phyir //
NK032(khi)001:168: bsam zhing brtags te gang la dmigs //
NK032(khi)001:169: dmigs med chos sku mtha' dang bral //
NK032(khi)001:171: klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)001:172: don gyi snying po bstan pa'i le'u'o //
NK032(khi)001:173: de ltar rdzogs pa chen po nang klong sde la /
NK032(khi)001:174: klong dgu bam po nyi khri chig stong du grags
NK032(khi)001:175: pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i mthar thug pa ni klong
NK032(khi)001:176: chen rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud yin la /
NK032(khi)001:177: de'i snying por gyur pa ni don gyi snying po
NK032(khi)001:178: bstan pa'i le'u bzhi pa 'di yin par gsungs pas
NK032(khi)001:179: khol du phyungs na sa yig rnying ltar sa bcad
NK032(khi)001:180: mdo tsam mchan du bgyis pa ste /
NK032(khi)001:181: rgyas par slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa'i
